# Personal GitHub
Host github.com
  HostName github.com
  User git
  IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_ed25519
  AddKeysToAgent yes
  UseKeychain yes
  IdentitiesOnly yes

# IntuitiveAI GitHub
Host github-intuitiveai
  HostName github.com
  User git
  IdentityFile ~/.ssh/id_ed25519_intuitiveai
  AddKeysToAgent yes
  UseKeychain yes
  IdentitiesOnly yes

